    <text xml:id="Site_WFY_Section_Gb_Cave125">
        <body>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="zh">
                <head>125號窟</head>
                <div>
                    <head>概述</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>位置</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>北岩，<foreign xml:lang="en">G</foreign>區（<ptr target="Fig_23_DSC_5193_stitch.jpg"/>）。</item>
                            <item>
                                <foreign xml:lang="en">f</foreign>壁方向：148°。</item>
                        </list>
                        <p>位於臥佛以東150米處，一條自北面過來，通向臥佛溝的舊路從窟前經過。窟底距現今路面約6至7米。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>形制</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>中型敞口方形窟，雙層窟口(<ptr target="Fig_26_DSC07202.jpg"/>)。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>尺寸</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>外窟口頂部較內窟窟頂高出20釐米。</item>
                            <item>外窟口東壁進深40釐米。</item>
                            <item>內窟口高約205、寬約208釐米，窟室進深東壁196、西壁236釐米。</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>保存狀況</head>
                        <p>窟室壁面僅初步鑿平，滿布鑿痕，未經打磨，亦未刊刻經文。2012年，該窟被用於堆放柴草。</p>
                        <ab>
                            <abbr>雷德侯</abbr>
                        </ab>
                        <figure rend="center" n="figure" xml:id="Fig_26_DSC07202.jpg">
                            <head xml:lang="zh">
                                <hi rend="bold">125</hi>號窟；2010年拍攝</head>
                            <head>Cave <hi rend="bold">125</hi>; photograph taken in 2010</head>
                            <graphic url="Fig_26_DSC07202.jpg"/>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="cave" xml:lang="en">
                <head>Cave 125</head>
                <div>
                    <head>Description</head>
                    <div>
                        <head>Location</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Northern slope, section G (fig. <ptr target="Fig_23_DSC_5193_stitch.jpg"/>).</item>
                            <item>Direction of wall f: 148˚.</item>
                        </list>
                        <p>Located 150 m to the east of the figure of the reclining Buddha. West of the
                            old path leading down into the valley from the north. Floor ca. 6-7 m above the present walkway.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Shape</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Box-shaped, standard size, with open front and double frame (fig. <ptr target="Fig_26_DSC07202.jpg"/>).</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>Measurements</head>
                        <list>
                            <item>Height of upper reveal: 20 cm.</item>
                            <item>Depth of eastern reveal: 40 cm.</item>
                            <item>Entrance opening circa 205 × 200 cm, depth 190 cm at eastern wall and 236 cm at western wall.</item>
                        </list>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <head>State of preservation</head>
                        <p>Walls scraped, but not polished; no engraved texts; in 2012 used for
                            storing wood.</p>
                        <ab>
                            <abbr>LL</abbr>
                        </ab>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
